title: Google\Cloud\SecurityCenter\V1\File
name: File
description:
File information about the related binary/library used by an executable, or the script used by a script interpreter

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.securitycenter.v1.File

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.path
params.description: Absolute path of the file as a JSON encoded string.

params.name: data.sha256
params.description: SHA256 hash of the first hashed_size bytes of the file encoded as a hex string. If hashed_size == size, sha256 represents the SHA256 hash of the entire file.

params.name: data.hashed_size
params.description: The length in bytes of the file prefix that was hashed. If hashed_size == size, any hashes reported represent the entire file.

params.name: data.partially_hashed
params.description: True when the hash covers only a prefix of the file.

params.name: data.contents
params.description: Prefix of the file contents as a JSON encoded string. (Currently only populated for Malicious Script Executed findings.)
